-- Kingfisher Sales Slip 0.8% in 10 Weeks to July 10 on Like-for-Like Basis
-- Angela Cullen
-- 2010-07-22T06:06:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/kingfisher-sales-slip-0-8-in-10-weeks-to-july-10-on-like-for-like-basis.html

          
          
             Kingfisher Plc said sales in the 10
weeks to July 10 declined 0.8 percent on a like-for-like basis,
and rose 0.3 percent in constant currencies.  
 “Our expectations for first-half cash and profit outturn
remain on track,” it said in a statement today.  
          
          


  


        